{"tid":2487302,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大家鍾意實體書多啲定電子書多啲","createTime":"2021-04-13T12:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T13:36:31.000Z","uid":370062,"like":20,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0783fde0e605ef1ddfd6e3e3956e92e2de22e866","tid":2487302,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"實體書好處：有件實物可以掂下，成排擺喺書櫃好好j，收藏啲書好有滿足感，手頭緊可以放返出去<br />\n電子書好處：平過實體書，慳位，隨時隨地有得睇，方便買唔洗驚冇貨<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實體：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電子：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c16ae7fcaa8fed8252c0618db37c8c5a359ca07","tid":2487302,"uid":305269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"輕小說教科書電子，其他實體"},{"pid":"7adde96897379bb0db2b1d83c39009a5bca63451","tid":2487302,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"實體書<br />\n幾鍾意浸味<br />\n每本書都有獨特既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb129d9dd0534f69af5a9ce4f8d05182c02d917","tid":2487302,"uid":229502,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"實體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電子書睇幾個鐘會壞眼，同啲排版硬係好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇實體書嗰種接觸感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4603467fe8774ffa529923be73ad08953a54eb","tid":2487302,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"實體"},{"pid":"e0317c86b50e5643be0f05498153d35ab4147265","tid":2487302,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"利申：我揀實體"},{"pid":"b8ae7bcb08a1f9ae71f92cddb54a1e66192ecdf2","tid":2487302,"uid":39072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit